<article id="post-998" class="post-998 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-costa-rica category-general tag-moving">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/06/t-minus-5-days/" rel="bookmark">T minus 5 days</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I&#8217;m beginning to know what a shuttle launch must feel like. Anxiety about what could go wrong, the knowledge that once the launch happens that there is little to do but hang on, that when you&#8217;re in orbit you&#8217;re pretty much at the mercy of your own fate.<br />
The key difference is that my feet will (for the most part) be on solid ground. (Well, except when I&#8217;m flying.) But otherwise I&#8217;m feeling pretty wound up about what&#8217;s going to happen shortly.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/06/t-minus-5-days/#more-998" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;T minus 5 days&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/06/t-minus-5-days/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2008-06-10T22:38:04-06:00">10 June 2008</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/costa-rica/" rel="category tag">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/moving/" rel="tag">moving</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/06/t-minus-5-days/#comments">2 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on T minus 5 days</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
