<article id="post-977" class="post-977 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-costa-rica category-general tag-avalon-country-club tag-condo tag-san-jose tag-santa-ana">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/05/finding-a-costa-rican-casa-day-2/" rel="bookmark">Finding a Costa Rican Casa, Day 2</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I knew today was going to be awkward when I woke up. Based on the conversation I&#8217;d had with Alex last night, none of the houses we&#8217;d seen on Day 1 were at all suitable. Either way too large, in not-so-nice areas (e.g. you&#8217;d feel like you couldn&#8217;t go anywhere), or had stairs (which we&#8217;re trying to avoid with our almost-walking infant).<br />
When Luz Elena and Lina Maria arrived this morning, I took their carefully crafted plan, opened the window, and tossed it out. (Figuratively speaking, of course.)<br />
It was time to get a little more serious.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/05/finding-a-costa-rican-casa-day-2/#more-977" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Finding a Costa Rican Casa, Day 2&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/05/finding-a-costa-rican-casa-day-2/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2008-05-27T22:12:39-06:00">27 May 2008</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/costa-rica/" rel="category tag">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/avalon-country-club/" rel="tag">avalon country club</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/condo/" rel="tag">condo</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/san-jose/" rel="tag">san jose</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/santa-ana/" rel="tag">santa ana</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/05/finding-a-costa-rican-casa-day-2/#comments">7 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Finding a Costa Rican Casa, Day 2</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
